{"tid":580784,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［秒經］ex有左另一半 心情好忐忑","createTime":"2018-03-04T19:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T20:33:25.000Z","uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b56c77a33f8fcc4e3d81574e8e03816a1137eee","tid":580784,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:01:20.000Z","msg":"雖然係我講分手 但原因係真係唔夾同無將來<br />\n所以我忍唔住先開口<br />\n拍左三年拖，我真係第一次忍唔住講分手<br />\n我以為佢點都會挽留我<br />\n但佢無，所以我都覺得佢其實已經唔再好似以前咁愛我<br />\n咁我覺得既然係咁，證明我都無分錯手吖<br />\n<br />\n然後過左三個月，依家佢有新女朋友了<br />\n我以為我放低左<br />\n點知個心點都係會有啲酸<br />\n搞到我一個人既時候，都唔知可以點<br />\n好想抒發哩種感覺，好壓抑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非基藍絲"},{"pid":"c0035fb416f62696de6584aee0e095f91c704308","tid":580784,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:03:43.000Z","msg":"life goes on be strong"},{"pid":"301820d0a76534679572ed7b8cec877a173a8e43","tid":580784,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:05:48.000Z","msg":"咁你又分手 矛盾"},{"pid":"508460a780240bcbd7a06e03d08b955c2aa2ffac","tid":580784,"uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"301820d0a76534679572ed7b8cec877a173a8e43","tid":580784,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:05:48.000Z","msg":"咁你又分手 矛盾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:09:08.000Z","msg":"唔分手又頂唔順<br />\n分左但又有啲唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知有啲矛盾<br />\n所以先上黎叫下春"},{"pid":"7a9b1effeec255cda741a743f73baabf5f785b58","tid":580784,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:10:20.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"b0c183222e52e70c00a1e3800aee7b54828b20c2","tid":580784,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:11:09.000Z","msg":"正常嘅，分手幾多年其實都會有感覺<br />\n愛過呀嘛<br />\n慢慢習慣啦"},{"pid":"6339eaca22a8981e44a215aa36148f231cfefe8d","tid":580784,"uid":115397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係無話會有100%夾的情侶，呢啲都係大家遷就，同埋將來都係要大家努力得返黎。<br />\n如果你真係要等一個100%夾同有將來的情人，我諗你呢世都未必有機會等到。"},{"pid":"10bdfa65ae22d32d1bb6baf80437827cd195cbd3","tid":580784,"uid":148835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:18:52.000Z","msg":"有冇右？"},{"pid":"6884ee4774157809a6b94e698a0d5008ac9e7676","tid":580784,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:23:09.000Z","msg":"過多排無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164eb3bae56098836f04f929f195e5f0376be118","tid":580784,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6339eaca22a8981e44a215aa36148f231cfefe8d","tid":580784,"uid":115397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"呢個世界真係無話會有100%夾的情侶，呢啲都係大家遷就，同埋將來都係要大家努力得返黎。<br />\n如果你真係要等一個100%夾同有將來的情人，我諗你呢世都未必有機會等到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:25:00.000Z","msg":"我嗰陣就係覺得佢無努力<br />\n所以分手前幾個月同佢講過哩個問題<br />\n到隔左幾個月都係咁我先講分手<br />\n佢話：你之前都講過哩個問題，所以我諗我地真係唔夾<br />\n但我真係唔見得佢嗰幾個月有努力試過<br />\n所以可能因為咁我唔忿氣掛"},{"pid":"0c9762d73f048af4ef90afd9665e8dbfc64a02a6","tid":580784,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6884ee4774157809a6b94e698a0d5008ac9e7676","tid":580784,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:23:09.000Z","msg":"過多排無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望快啲過"},{"pid":"6b4ad6eb74aab42ae9e298bcb5495849cbfe3f99","tid":580784,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:27:07.000Z","msg":"咁岩既<br />\n我ex最近又有左另一半<br />\n心酸緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1876b97963bb647e6b1615cd1e9f476025c8b9e0","tid":580784,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4ad6eb74aab42ae9e298bcb5495849cbfe3f99","tid":580784,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:27:07.000Z","msg":"咁岩既<br />\n我ex最近又有左另一半<br />\n心酸緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:56:04.000Z","msg":"唔想諗<br />\n但一個人嗰陣又自然會好多野諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff4b9a52076daa8fdbd9122ecca18e8043095f8","tid":580784,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T20:33:25.000Z","msg":"沒有這件事，妨礙我們<br />\n難道我和你，又會一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}